.checkbox
  %label(for="resize")
    %input(type="checkbox" id="resize" name="resize" value="32x32") 
    Resize* the image to attempt to make the filesize smaller.

%br

%input.btn.btn-primary.btn-lg(type="submit" value="GOGOGOGOGOGOGOGO")

%hr

.help-block * The image will be resized to 32x32, but the aspect ratio will be retained, so you may up with an image with dimensions 32x12 or 10x32 for example.
